{"tid":420903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰隆尼亞獨立公投 蘇格蘭首席大臣對衝突場景表關切","createTime":"2017-10-01T18:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T23:03:44.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdc6e23051d6f429bf3af9bd3434ac1953afeb3","tid":420903,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區10月1日舉行獨立公投，且有460人在與公投相關的警民衝突中受傷，蘇格首蘭首席大臣史德金呼籲西班牙政府「改變作法」，表示「加泰隆尼亞出現的畫面越來越令人關切」。<br />\n西班牙鎮暴警察強行進入多處投票所，並對抗議民眾發射橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n史德金在推特網站推文說：「無論我們對獨立的觀點為何，所有人都應譴責我們見到的場景，在此呼籲西班牙在有人受重傷前改變作法。」<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭2014年曾就蘇獨舉行公投，公投結果為45% 的人主張脫離英國，55%的人選擇留在英國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2734396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2734396&d=tkwyi1jOJc%2BMdYw2O9tY%2FTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2e9f95f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2734396</a>"},{"pid":"5200b7bb8bcc999fd2c6343456194728033ef1a9","tid":420903,"uid":33686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"到底佢係遣責警察打人定係公投呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ed81b32ef4ab571f5cf3b2e21ad1b47622dd9","tid":420903,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭示範左點做會成功<br />\n<br />\n加泰示範左點做係唔會成功"},{"pid":"dd29ce4f3e6c5c514bc79e6c1678d63ec6ec4178","tid":420903,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底佢係遣責警察打人定係公投呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明顯屌西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bf35222e2e220417ca3dc81dbe668f0b3b125a","tid":420903,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T23:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到底佢係遣責警察打人定係公投呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明顯屌西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n華媒睇死人"}]}